<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="often-adv">often <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɒfn,'ɒftən/    美 /'ɔːfn,'ɔftən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-frequently">1.★ <strong>经常；通常 (frequently)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>How often</strong> do you listen to live music?
你多久听一次现场音乐？</p><footer>外研⑥ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you fly <strong>quite / very often</strong> for your job?
你的工作需要经常坐飞机吗？</p><footer>2010 广东</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="more-often-than-not-as-often-as-not">more often than not / as often as not</h3>
<p>1.<strong>通常；往往</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I wonder how <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ you’ll water this kind of flower.
— Every other day.  （2009 四川改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. often  </p></div>